Class AntiTheftMailSenderService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • com.innolabs.spydroid.AntiTheftMailSenderService

  • public class AntiTheftMailSenderService
extends Service
    AntiTheft Mail Sender Service is a Service that sends the After Theft details to the user either by e-mail or SMS.
